i## Little hack	/	tilde.team	70
i	/	tilde.team	70
iTo avoid having to manage all the packages by hand, I	/	tilde.team	70
idecided to install a package manager, but not just any	/	tilde.team	70
ipackage manager, Nix. It will allow me to have fully	/	tilde.team	70
ifunctional immutable packages.	/	tilde.team	70
hNix	URL:https://github.com/NixOS/nix	github.com	443
i	/	tilde.team	70
iI installed it with the DeterminateSystems installer.	/	tilde.team	70
hDeterminateSystems	URL:https://github.com/DeterminateSystems/nix-installer	github.com	443
i	/	tilde.team	70
iIt allowed me to build very complicated packages such as	/	tilde.team	70
iFirefox, here's a preview.	/	tilde.team	70
hFirefox	URL:https://www.mozilla.org/fr/firefox	www.mozilla.org	443
i	/	tilde.team	70
i/lfs_firefox.png	/	tilde.team	70
